name: Bruno's Pasta
description: Bruno's - Pasta Sauce has a very high nutritional value, is moderately processed, and is estimated to have a low carbon footprint and a low water footprint.

name: Doritos
description: Corn, Vegetable Oil (Corn, Canola, And/or Sunflower Oil), Maltodextrin (Made From Corn), Salt, Cheddar Cheese (Milk, Cheese Cultures, Salt, Enzymes), Whey, Monosodium Glutamate, Buttermilk, Romano Cheese (Part-skim Cow's Milk, Cheese Cultures, Salt, Enzymes), Whey Protein Concentrate, Onion Powder, Corn Flour, Natural

name: Almaral Milk
description: Water, Milk Solids, Emulsifier: Vegetable Oil Origin (E471), Stabilizers (E407 and E412), Niacin, Vitamin E, Zinc Pantothenic Acid, Vitamin a, Vitamin D3, Vitamin B6, Vitamin B2, Thiamine, Folic Acid, Vitamin K1, Biotin, Vitamin B12.

name: Alpro Almond Milk
description: Water, Almond (2.3%), Sugar, Calcium (Tri-calcium phosphate), Sea salt, Stabilisers (Locust bean gum, Gellan gum), Emulsifier (Lecithins (Sunflower)), Natural flavouring, Vitamins (B2, B12, E, D2).

name: IBERIA Oil
description: The bottle actually contains a blend comprised of 80 percent sunflower oil and 20 percent EVOO, according to the ingredients list on the back.

name: Goya Veg Oil
description: GOYA® Vegetable Oil is made from 100% USA-grown soybeans. Its neutral flavor and aroma allow the full flavors of your dishes to stand out. Use it to cook, fry, in baking and to make delicious dressings and sauces. It has no trans fat or cholesterol, and contains omega-3s.

name: Sprite
description: Carbonated Water, Sugar, Acids (Citric Acid, Tartaric Acid), Acidity Regulator (Sodium Citrates), Sweeteners (Acesulfame-K, Aspartame), Natural Lemon And Lime Flavourings.

name: Dew
description: CARBONATED WATER, HIGH FRUCTOSE CORN SYRUP, CONCENTRATED ORANGE JUICE, CITRIC ACID, NATURAL FLAVOR, SODIUM BENZOATE (PRESERVES FRESHNESS), CAFFEINE, SODIUM CITRATE, GUM ARABIC, ERYTHORBIC ACID (PRESERVES FRESHNESS), CALCIUM DISODIUM EDTA (TO PROTECT FLAVOR), YELLOW 5.

name: SevenUp
description: Nothing can Lift UP your day like the crisp and refreshing taste of 7UP. Ingredients Filtered Carbonated Water, Citric Acid, Potassium Citrate, Potassium Benzoate (Preservative), Aspartame, Acesulfame Potassium, Natural Flavor, Calcium Disodium EDTA (to Protect Flavor).

name: Coka Cola
description: Carbonated water – Approximately 90% of Coca-Cola is water. ... Sugar – Coca-Cola Classic's sweet taste (and also some of its mouthfeel) comes from sugar. ... Caramel colour – A very specific caramel is made especially for Coca-Cola, to give the drink its characteristic colour.

name: Pepsi
description: Carbonated Water, Sugar, Colour (Caramel E150d), Acid (Phosphoric Acid), Flavourings (including Caffeine), Sweeteners (Acesulfame K, Sucralose).

name: Fanta
description: Carbonated Water, Orange Fruit from Concentrate (4%), Citric Acid, Sweeteners (Acesulfame K, Aspartame), Preservative (Potassium Sorbate), Malic Acid, Natural Orange Flavouring with Other Natural Flavourings, Vegetable Concentrates (Carrot, Pumpkin), Antioxidant (Ascorbic Acid), Stabiliser (Guar Gum).

name: Cheese
description: Cheese is a dairy product produced in wide ranges of flavors, textures, and forms by coagulation of the milk protein casein. It comprises proteins and fat from milk (usually the milk of cows, buffalo, goats, or sheep).

name: Meat
description: Meat is defined as the flesh of animals (including fishes and birds) used as food, that can be part of a healthful diet. Meat is a major source of key nutrients, such as high-quality protein, iron, and B vitamins for many Americans.

name: Barilla Farfalle Pasta
description: Farfalle, which means “butterfly” in Italian, are rectangular or oval pieces of pasta that are pinched in the middle. Barilla® Farfalle is made with non-GMO ingredients.

name: Orange Flower
description: Radiant and warm, the orange flower bursts with lively energy. Its vibrant petals exude a cheerful glow, creating a captivating spectacle that symbolizes enthusiasm and creativity in nature's palette

name: Pink Flower
description: Blooming in delicate shades of pink, this charming flower showcases tender petals, radiating grace and warmth. A symbol of love and admiration, it captivates with its soft hue and gentle allure

name: Red Flower
description: In the garden of vibrant hues, the red flower stands bold and passionate. Its velvety petals exude a timeless elegance, evoking love and intensity in a captivating display of natural beauty

name: Blue Flower
description: Nestled in nature's embrace, the blue flower unfolds with serene elegance. Its petals, a tranquil symphony of blue hues, create a soothing spectacle, invoking calm and a sense of peaceful beauty
